---
source: crates/runtime/tests/metadata/mod.rs
expression: explain_met_all_location_filtered
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: met_all.id ASC NULLS LAST, met_all.location ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |   BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |     TableScan: met_all projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified, location, size], full_filters=[met_all.location = Utf8("s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet")] |
| physical_plan | SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST, location@6 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                                                                      |
|               |   BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |     ParquetExec: file_groups={1 group: [[hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet]]}, projection=[id, value, year, month, day, last_modified, location, size]                                                   |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
